 Project Overview
A modern Flutter mobile application for credit monitoring with beautiful authentication screens and smooth user experience.

- Features
Splash Screen with scale and fade animations
Login Screen with email/password validation
Signup Screen with comprehensive form validation
Responsive Design for all screen sizes
Success Bottom Sheets for user feedback
Modern UI with background images and smooth transitions

- project Structure
 i shoose clean architecture for better maintainability and scalability. Here is the proposed structure:
lib/
├── main.dart
├── Auth
    ├── components/         # Reusable components for authentication screens
    │── pages
        ├── splash_screen.dart     # Animated splash screen
        ├── login_screen.dart      # Login with validation
        └── signup_screen.dart     # Signup with confirmation

 --Design Specifications
 Primary Color: #1E3A8A (Blue)
 Background: White
 Text: Black87 & Grey
 Success: Green


 --Typography
 Font Family: Inter
 Headers: 32px Bold
 Body: 16px Regular
 Labels: 14px Medium

--Prerequisites
 Flutter SDK 3.0+
 Android Studio
 Android Emulator or Device

 --Installation
 Implementation Details
 Splash Screen
 Duration: 3 seconds

 --Animations: Scale + Fade

 --Navigation: Auto-redirect to Login

-- Login Screen
 Fields:
 Email (with format validation)
 Password (min 6 characters, letters & numbers)
 Forgot Password link

 Validation Rules:
 Email must be valid format
 Password required, min 6 chars
 Real-time validation feedback

 --Signup Screen
 Fields:

 Full Name (required)
 Email (valid format)
 Password (min 6 chars, letters & numbers)
 Confirm Password (must match)
 Validation Rules:
 All fields required
 Email must be valid
 Password strength enforced
 Password match verification

---Testing
 Test Checklist
 Splash animation works
 Login form validation
 Signup form validation
 Navigation between screens
 Success bottom sheets
 Responsive design
 Keyboard handling
 Loading states

 Run Tests
 bash
 # Run on Android emulator
 flutter run

 # Test on device
 flutter run -d <device_id>


 - Screens Overview
 1. Splash Screen
 App logo & name
 Animated entrance

 2. Login Screen
 Background image with overlay
 Email & password fields
 Forgot password link
 Signup navigation
 Form validation

 3. Signup Screen
 Background image with overlay
 Full registration form
 Password confirmation
 Back to login navigation
 Comprehensive validation

 --------User Flows--------
 Successful Login Flow
 Splash Screen (3 sec)
 Login Screen → Enter credentials
 Validation passed → Show loading
 Success bottom sheet → Continue to app

 Successful Signup Flow
 Splash Screen → Login Screen
 Tap "Sign Up" → Signup Screen
 Fill form → Validation passed

 Success bottom sheet → Redirect to login

 State Management
 Local state using setState()

 Form validation with GlobalKey<FormState>

 Loading states with _isLoading boolean

 Password visibility toggles

Responsive Design
 Flexible padding and margins
 Adaptive font sizes
 Scrollable content for small screens
 Keyboard-aware layouts

--- Performance Features
 Optimized animations
 Efficient widget rebuilding
 Proper disposal of controllers
 Memory leak prevention

 Support
 ---For issues during implementation:
 Check Flutter version compatibility
 Verify font files are properly linked
 Ensure Android emulator is running
 Check console for specific error messages
 Delivery: Complete Flutter source code with all screens implemented and tested on Android.

